TITLE: Initializing Unipile Client in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Creates a new UnipileClient instance with the provided DSN and access token for authentication.
SOURCE: https://github.com/unipile/unipile-node-sdk/blob/develop/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { UnipileClient } from 'unipile-node-sdk';

const client = new UnipileClient('https://{YOUR_DSN}', '{YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN}');
```

