TITLE: Creating Hosted Auth Link in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Generates a hosted authentication link for connecting multiple accounts with various parameters.
SOURCE: https://github.com/unipile/unipile-node-sdk/blob/develop/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
await client.account.createHostedAuthLink({
  type: 'create', // or reconnect
  expiresOn: '2024-12-22T12:00:00.701Z',
  api_url: 'your api',
  providers: '*', // * means all provider
  success_redirect_url: 'your success url',
  failure_redirect_url: 'your fail url',
  notify_url: 'your notify url',
});
```

