TITLE: Using Unpackaged Endpoint in Unipile Node SDK
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to use the "Get raw data" route for endpoints not included in the SDK. It demonstrates sending a POST request to the LinkedIn API.
SOURCE: https://github.com/unipile/unipile-node-sdk/blob/develop/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const client = new UnipileClient(BASE_URL, "ACCESS_TOKEN", {});
await client.request.send({
  path: ["linkedin"],
  method: "POST",
  parameters: { account_id: "!!YOURACCOUNTID!!" },
  body: {
    "body": {"patch":{"$set":{"following":true}}},
    "account_id": "dfR-rG0tQfGhfeP2l5_Bdw",
    "method": "POST",
    "request_url": "https://www.linkedin.com/voyager/api/feed/dash/followingStates/urn:li:fsd_followingState:urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAcDMMQBODyLwZrRcgYhrkCafURGqva0U4E",
    "encoding": false
  },
});
```

