TITLE: Sending InMail with LinkedIn API in Unipile Node SDK
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to send an InMail (message to people outside users' network) using the LinkedIn API through the Unipile Node SDK.
SOURCE: https://github.com/unipile/unipile-node-sdk/blob/develop/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
await client.messaging.startNewChat({
  account_id: 't5XY4yQzR9WVrlNFyzPMhw',
  attendees_ids: ['user provider id'],
  text: 'send a inmail',
  options: {
    linkedin: {
      api: 'classic' // recruiter / sales_navigator
      inmail: true,
    },
  },
});
```

